headline: XTANDI® Plus Leuprolide Reduced Risk of Death by 40% vs Leuprolide Alone in Men with a Type of Advanced Prostate Cancer
summary: NEW YORK & NORTHBROOK, Ill., October 19, 2025--Pfizer Inc. (NYSE: PFE) and Astellas Pharma U.S. Inc. headline: Pfizer’s BRAFTOVI® + MEKTOVI® Shows Sustained Long-Term Survival in Patients with Advanced Lung Cancer
summary: NEW YORK, October 19, 2025--Pfizer Inc. (NYSE: PFE) today announced updated follow-up results from the single-arm Phase 2 PHAROS trial evaluating BRAFTOVI® (encorafenib) + MEKTOVI® (binimetinib) for the treatment of adults with metastatic non-small cell lung cancer (mNSCLC) with a BRAF V600E mutation.
